"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931044-rafael-nadal-2024-Paris-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael Nadalhas revealed his short-term plans after being knocked out of the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 98, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 97, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday, Nadal and partner Carlos Alcarazlost 6-2 6-4 to the fourth-seeded American duoof Austin Krajicek and Rajeev Ram, ending the icon's hopes of a fairytale finish.\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998236132516205, \"rank\": 0.0001747907856086306, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Austin Krajicek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajeev Ram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his final summer Games, Nadal was already out of the individual event after beaing beaten byNovak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.950339560403546e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old has already returned to his home in Mallorca, and has spoken out on his future.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCD_Mallorca\", \"score\": 0.9894545379326798, \"rank\": 0.010657719871787014, \"text\": \"Mallorca\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCD_Mallorca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCD_Mallorca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's time to rest and take some time,\\\" he toldIB3 TV.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And in a few days I will be able to analyse everything these months have been and know what I really want.\\\"\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal is widely expected to retire ahead of the 2025 season, but is yet to confirm the date when he plans to walk away.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His latest comments however, suggest a decision could be pending.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The match at Court Philippe Chatrier, the same stadium where Nadal has won his record 14French Opentitles, could yet prove his last.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}, {\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}, {\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.950339560403546e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a capacity crowd seemed aware of the possibility as they created a partisan atmosphere in favour of the 'King of Clay'.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    The 'Nadalcaraz' partnership had been considered a dream one by tennis fans, with the all-time great alongside the sport's newest star.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite missing out on a fitting end to his Olympic legacy, the 22-time Grand Slam champion insisted he enjoyed his experience in Paris.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983938324, \"rank\": 1.6060273196151862e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And onInstagram, he thanked his compatriot, who has since won through to the semi-finals of the indivudual event.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you Carlitos for these days, which were fantastic in many ways,\\\" he wrote.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlitos_(footballer,_born_1982)\", \"score\": 0.9649193813828921, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlitos\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlitos_(footballer,_born_1982)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlitos_(footballer,_born_1982)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unforgettable experience with you and the whole team.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And now most importantly, let us go for the medal, you are closer after today, you can achieve it.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all with you!\\\"\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Swiatek offers excuse for Olympics loss before walking out of interview in tears  Do not miss:Swiatek refuses to shake umpire's hand at Olympics and abandons interview to cry  Do not miss:'Scared' tennis star snubbed Olympics for same reason as Emma Raducanu  Alcaraz is two games away from emulating Nadal, who won gold at the 2008 Olympics in Beijing.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.404662115047925e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\